        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-white text-4xl md:text-6xl max-w-sm">Snakebite Mitigation Program</h1>
            <p class="text-white text-lg">The only feasible mitigation is to learn to live with them safely, learn proper snakebite management measures including first aid, and using modern medical facilities for treatment.</p>
            <br>
            <a href="/payments?type=1" class="my-6 bg-white text-black py-2 px-4 border-b-4 border-white-700 border-solid rounded">Donate to this cause</a>
